{"tid":225820,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"好多連登仔都唔識分呢兩隻字","createTime":"2017-05-02T05:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T03:35:17.000Z","uid":107938,"like":43,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b71cc8ba426164802f408762f775687874a6ea7","tid":225820,"uid":107938,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T05:19:57.000Z","msg":"我發覺好多連登仔都分唔到呢兩隻字。<br />\n<br />\n梗<br />\n讀音：收ng尾<br />\n例詞：梗係(而唔係緊係) <br />\n<br />\n緊<br />\n讀音：收n尾<br />\n例詞：做緊嘢(而唔係做梗嘢)<br />\n<br />\n屌5p字唔緊要，不過唔好自己又寫錯字，仲要係因為懶音而引起嘅錯字。次次見到梗緊都分唔到真係真心嬲。"},{"pid":"dd9d882cba5e1943f1e4b3544536f54b70d3b3ad","tid":225820,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T05:22:03.000Z","msg":"長知識了"},{"pid":"e04d7bdd48c49a0fc4e49d847114e490159b54be","tid":225820,"uid":107938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T05:23:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>長知識了</blockquote><br />\n認真，我個輩好少人分唔到，係咪我太老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e231c4c94f8fef62ff0121ece506c58a2f8ffd10","tid":225820,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T05:38:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5acbc83f3548311d4939de7876568cf03fd23f29","tid":225820,"uid":107938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T05:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢兩個字唔同音班垃圾都分唔到<br />\n但班垃圾就去屌人打同音異字</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31329004c4f2b8eaf51549017e5abf35b7cc728b","tid":225820,"uid":107938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T06:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ca2e411ec2bbf2acb85fe6f5a90e1e03cfc632","tid":225820,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢兩個字唔同音班垃圾都分唔到<br />\